{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "绯龙的火山 第3章 3-6 火山即将喷发",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "绯龙催促一行人赶快逃跑，\\n只身飞向火山口阻止火山喷发。\\n但是王子无法放任受伤的绯龙不管，\\n于是紧随其后。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "telop",
            "context": "\\n阿德拉火山\\n熔岩洞窟 最深处\\n \\n ",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "绯龙",
            "context": "真是的……\\n竟然被人类保护着醒来，\\n今天净是些让我受打击的事！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "醒来就好……\\n已经没事了吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "不，只是应急处理。\\n现在依旧处于危险状态。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "库菈乌，谢谢你努力治疗。\\n稍微休息一下吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "绯龙",
            "context": "唔，奇怪的人类……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "绯龙",
            "context": "然后呢，你们一路追到这里，\\n到底有什么企图？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_1001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "没有什么企图。\\n我只是来救你的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_1002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "绯龙",
            "context": "救我……\\n哼，还在说这种话。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "唔哦哦哦！\\n怎、怎么晃得这么厉害！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "不会又要喷发了吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "绯龙",
            "context": "魔力这么紊乱……\\n好像闹得有点过头了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "大闹成这样，\\n岂止是“有点”！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "现在可不是发呆的时候。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "要是火山喷发，\\n我们就束手无策了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "赶紧离开这里去避难吧！\\n绯龙，你也得马上逃！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "绯龙",
            "context": "这剧烈的摇晃……\\n放弃吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "绯龙",
            "context": "在你们都逃出去之前\\n就会喷发的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "咦！等、等一下！\\n这可不行！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "龙也无能为力吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "绯龙",
            "context": "唉……真拿你们没办法。\\n我就来阻止喷发吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "阻止喷发？\\n那种事也能办到？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "绯龙",
            "context": "火山口就在深处。\\n那里就是这片土地的魔力集中地！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "绯龙",
            "context": "要在火山口纠正紊乱的魔力。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "绯龙",
            "context": "这样一来这片土地的魔力就会安定，\\n喷发自然也会平息。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "纠正紊乱的魔力……\\n那种事做得到吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "绯龙",
            "context": "当然。龙就是掌管魔力的存在。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "绯龙",
            "context": "这里的魔力就如我身体的一部分。\\n可别太小看我了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "绯龙",
            "context": "那么，再见了。\\n你们赶紧找出口逃出去吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "咦……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "喂喂……\\n绯龙这家伙跑了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "喂！赶快逃啊！那家伙说得没错。\\n得赶快逃离这里！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_1003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不，那样的话即使我们得救了，\\n绯龙也很危险。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_1004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "就算是再强大的龙，\\n身负重伤的情况下要阻止火山喷发……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_1005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我说纳姆，\\n你可以追踪飞走的绯龙吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "咦！？\\n唔，靠气味的话也不是不可能。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "快带我们去！\\n绯龙的伤还没有痊愈，不能放任不管！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "的确，绯龙是在逞强。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "以现在的状态，\\n很可能会被魔兽……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "好，我们去帮助绯龙\\n阻止火山喷发吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_1006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这是所有人都能得救的唯一方法！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_1007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "哎呀，你这个贪心的王子。\\n真拿你没办法，我们也奉陪到底吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_05_1008",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}